Deer Diary Commands
===================

This project provides a subset of Minecraft server-command functionality
(`/extinguish`, `/god`, `/invsee`, `/mute`, `/tp_offline`, `/kickme`,
`/leaderboard`, `/near`, `/rec`, `/jump`, `/rtp`, `/tpl`, `/tpx`) for the
Deer Diary modpack. It is a fresh implementation under the MIT License.

